    h1 Messagebar React Component
    ul.docs-index
    p Messagebar React component represents Framework7's <a href="../docs/messagebar.html">Messagebar</a> component.
    h2 Messagebar Components
    p There are following components included:
    ul
      li <code><b>Messagebar</b></code> / <code><b>F7Messagebar</b></code> - main messagebar element
      li <code><b>MessagebarSheet</b></code> / <code><b>F7MessagebarSheet</b></code> - messagebar sheet element
      li <code><b>MessagebarSheetImage</b></code> / <code><b>F7MessagebarSheetImage</b></code> - messagebar sheet image item
      li <code><b>MessagebarSheetItem</b></code> / <code><b>F7MessagebarSheetItem</b></code> - messagebar sheet item
      li <code><b>MessagebarAttachments</b></code> / <code><b>F7MessagebarAttachments</b></code> - messagebar attachments element
      li <code><b>MessagebarAttachment</b></code> / <code><b>F7MessagebarAttachment</b></code> - single messagebar attachment element
    p
      img(src=cdn + "/i/docs/messagebar-vue.jpg", style="max-width: 950px; width: 100%")
